; SAT: 4-bit shift register. Input bit shifts in from LSB.
; After 4 steps with input=1, register becomes 0b1111 = 15.
; Bad: reg == 15 (reachable at step 4)
; Expected: SAT
1 sort bitvec 4
2 sort bitvec 1
3 state 1 reg
4 zero 1
5 init 1 3 4
6 input 2 inp
7 constd 2 1
8 sll 1 3 7
9 uext 1 6
10 or 1 8 9
11 next 1 3 10
12 constd 1 15
13 sort bitvec 1
14 eq 13 3 12
15 bad 14
